        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Small Business Relief from Disease Induced Economic Hardship Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Small Business Act to expand the definition of a &quot;disaster&quot; for which the Small Business Administration may provide disaster loans to small business concerns to include communicable diseases for which the federal government issues a travel alert or travel warning.</p>  <p>]]></text>
